# Proposal

<createEntity class="com.acme.Person">
    <property name="name">Jane Doe</property>
    <property name="gender">FEMALE</property>
</createEntity>

<updateEntity class="com.acme.Person">
    <where>
        <and>
            <property name="name">Jane Doe</property>
            <property name="gender">FEMALE</property>
        </and>
    </where>
    <property name="name">John Doe</property>
    <property name="birthPlace">MALE</property>
</updateEntity>

<deleteEntity class="com.acme.Person">
    <where>
        <or>
            <property name="name">Jane Doe</property>
            <property name="name">John Doe</property>
        </or>
    </where>
</deleteEntity>

# Open questions

 - Batch import?
 - Beyond equality? (<, >, <=, >=, IN, NOT IN, !=, exists, not exists)
